01:43:45.344 --> 01:43:50.644
Clavier. But Bach wrote
profoundly beautiful music, and

01:43:52.204 --> 01:43:56.184
some of the most complex
contrapuntal music that

01:43:56.244 --> 01:43:59.864
I don't think anyone has
